    m_UnityText: {fileID: 0}
    m_TextMeshProText: {fileID: 0}
  m_DemoZones:
  - m_Zone: {fileID: 8976248820443050641}
    m_Header: Balance
    m_Sprite: {fileID: 0}
    m_Description: The Balance ability will keep the character oriented in the forward/backward
      direction of a narrow platform. The ability will restrict the character's rotation
      so they can only move forward or backwards along the object.
  - m_Zone: {fileID: 2354102126029631256}
    m_Header: Crawl
    m_Sprite: {fileID: 0}
    m_Description: The Crawl ability will play a crawling animation with the character
      moving on all four limbs.
  - m_Zone: {fileID: 3992739090533910304}
    m_Header: Dodge
    m_Sprite: {fileID: 0}
    m_Description: The Dodge ability will allow the character to quickly dodge left,
      right, forward or back in order to avoid an attack. Dodge by aiming at the
      target and pressing the Jump button.
  - m_Zone: {fileID: 4869672394586258067}
    m_Header: Hang
    m_Sprite: {fileID: 0}
    m_Description: The Hang ability allows the character to hang from flat objects.
      The hang ability is NOT able to climb up any object and is only designed for
      hanging.
  - m_Zone: {fileID: 5626622780712687858}
    m_Header: Ledge Strafe
    m_Sprite: {fileID: 0}
    m_Description: "The Ledge Strafe ability will play a strafing animation while
      the character is on a ledge. This ledge should be narrow to prevent\r the character
      from being able to walk normally across it. "
  - m_Zone: {fileID: 6185936827967496731}
    m_Header: Roll
    m_Sprite: {fileID: 0}
    m_Description: The Roll ability allows the character to play a rolling animation.
      A rolling animation can also play if the character falls from a tall object.
  - m_Zone: {fileID: 3817287520605908520}
    m_Header: Vault
    m_Sprite: {fileID: 0}
    m_Description: The Vault ability will allow the character to traverse over a
      vertical object.
